#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"Amazing team! smiling, always nice to talk with, they always have the best "
"advices for you, adapted to your needs!"
msgstr ""
"Fantastisk team! Smilende, altid hyggelige at tale med, de har altid de "
"bedste råd til dig, præcis til dine behov!"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_text_image
msgid "Are you thinking of selling?"
msgstr "Overvejer du at sælge?"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_text_block
msgid ""
"At <b>Odoo Travel Agency</b> our agents are more than a consultant, they are "
"fellow <b>travelers with a passion</b> to help you explore the world. With "
"more than 75 years combined experience you can be sure we are devoted to "
"finding the best solutions for your travel plans."
msgstr ""
"Hos <b>Odoo Rejsebureau</b> er vores medarbejdere mere end blot rådgivere – "
"de er <b>medrejsende med en passion</b> for at hjælpe dig med at opdage "
"verden. Med i alt mere end 75 års erfaring kan du være sikker på, at vi "
"finder de bedste løsninger til dine rejseplaner."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid ""
"At Real Estate Agency we have fixed price fees. This means we only charge "
"when your home sale is confirmed."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_image_text
msgid "Bored with your interior?"
msgstr "Er du træt af din indretning?"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_image_text
msgid ""
"Discover our tailor-made services to embellish the decoration of your home."
msgstr ""
"Oplev vores skræddersyede tjenester, der kan gøre dit hjem endnu smukkere."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Elegant, modern sophisticated architecture with an impressive in large scale "
"home designed with the finest imported finishes. Marble and wood floors..."
msgstr ""
"Elegant, moderne og raffineret arkitektur med et imponerende, rummeligt hus, "
"der er indrettet med interiør af allerhøjeste kvalitet. Marmor og trægulve "
"..."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_image_text
msgid "Explore our services"
msgstr "Lær mere om vores ydelser"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"From start to finish, they were extremely professional, friendly, helpful "
"and easy to do business with. Very happy with the experience and the company."
msgstr ""
"Fra start til slut var de yderst professionelle, venlige og hjælpsomme, og "
"det var nemt at samarbejde med dem. Jeg er meget tilfreds med oplevelsen og "
"virksomheden."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid "House On The Hill"
msgstr "Huset på bakken"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid ""
"Increase Visitor retention. Customer engagement on a website with virtual "
"tour is 5 times longer compared to a site without it."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid "Increased Visibility"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_text_image
msgid ""
"Make an appointment for a free valuation of your property. We visit the "
"property, advise you on a realistic asking price and we explain our way of "
"working. <br/>\n"
"        You can decide in all freedom whether or not you would like to work "
"with us for the sale of your property."
msgstr ""
"Aftal en tid til en gratis vurdering af din ejendom. Vi besigtiger "
"ejendommen, rådgiver dig om en realistisk pris og forklarer dig, hvordan vi "
"arbejder.<br/>\n"
"        Du kan i ro og mag beslutte, om du ønsker at samarbejde med os om "
"salget af din ejendom eller ej."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid "Moutain View"
msgstr "Udsigt til bjergene"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid "No fixed fees"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_banner
msgid ""
"Now you can find more than 5,000+ property choices with our professional "
"agents!<br/>"
msgstr ""
"Nu kan du finde mere end 5.000 ejendomsannoncer sammen med vores "
"professionelle ejendomsmæglere!<br/>"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_picture
msgid "Open your horizons"
msgstr "Udvid dine horisonter"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_image_text
msgid ""
"Our decoration experts are at your disposal to guide you step by step in the "
"design of your interior and will give you the best advice for your interior "
"design."
msgstr ""
"Vores indretningseksperter står til rådighed for at vejlede dig trin for "
"trin i indretningen af dit hjem og give dig de bedste råd til din indretning."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid "Paradise Residence"
msgstr "Paradise Residence"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"Positive energy, great team spirit, hard workers and awesome people! I "
"warmly recommend them!"
msgstr ""
"Positiv energi, fantastisk teamspirit, hårdtarbejdende medarbejdere og "
"skønne mennesker! Jeg kan på det varmeste anbefale dem!"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid "Premium Quality"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid "Pro Photo Shoot"
msgstr ""

