#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_picture
msgid "Property on the coasts of the Mediterranean."
msgstr "Ejendom ved Middelhavskysten."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_banner
msgid "See properties"
msgstr "Se egenskaber"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"The house is surrounded by garden terraces that create unique spaces and an "
"intimate ambience. With no overlooking neighbours, the garden offers real "
"privacy."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_real_estate.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Tema værktøjer"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid ""
"They say an image is worth a thousand words and we know you know how "
"important it is to have the best photography."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid "View details"
msgstr "Se detaljer"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_call_to_action
msgid "Want To Become A Real Estate Agent?"
msgstr "Vil du blive ejendomsmægler?"

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Waste no time in viewing this truly stunning property. The property's "
"surroundings really set it apart, offering idyllic sea views overlooking a "
"park."
msgstr ""
"Spild ikke tiden, men kom og se denne virkelig betagende ejendom. "
"Omgivelserne omkring ejendommen er helt unikke og byder på en idyllisk "
"havudsigt ud over en park."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_text_block
msgid ""
"We are <b>Odoo Travel Agency</b>, dedicated to making your vacation dreams "
"come true! Overwhelmed with too many choices on the internet? We offer you "
"answers, support, advice, and itineraries that will amaze you with their "
"<b>thoroughness and thoughtfulness</b>."
msgstr ""
"Vi er <b>Odoo Rejsebureau</b> og har sat os for at gøre dine feriedrømme til "
"virkelighed! Er du overvældet af de mange tilbud på internettet? Vi tilbyder "
"dig svar, hjælp, råd og rejseplaner, der vil overraske dig med deres <b>"
"grundighed og gennemtænkthed</b>."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid ""
"We are committed to delivering high quality services that enhance your brand "
"by allowing visitors to interact virtually."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_call_to_action
msgid "We'll help you to grow your career and growth."
msgstr "Vi hjælper dig med at udvikle din karriere og din personlige vækst."

#. module: theme_real_estate
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_real_estate.s_picture
msgid ""
"We’ve selected properties from all types and all areas.<br/>\n"
"        The house of your dreams is around the corner."
msgstr ""
"Vi har udvalgt ejendomme af alle slags og fra alle regioner.<br/>\n"
"        Dit drømmehus ligger lige rundt om hjørnet."

